{"id": "ner-010281", "text": "我跟你說喔，馬雲那場關於人工智慧的演講真的很精彩，他還特別提到思愛普跟 Slack 這類企業軟體未來的整合趨勢。", "register": "日常對話", "bucket": "S", "n_han": 46, "est_duration_s": 10.59, "has_english": true, "has_phonetic_entity": true, "n_substitutable": 3, "annotations": [{"surface": "馬雲", "entity_id": "people_intl:289", "start": 6, "end": 8, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "馬雲", "en": "Jack Ma", "aliases": ["Jack Ma"], "pinyin": "mǎ yún", "zhuyin": "ㄇㄚˇ ㄩㄣˊ"}, {"surface": "思愛普", "entity_id": "companies_intl:113", "start": 31, "end": 34, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "思愛普", "en": "SAP", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "sī ài pǔ", "zhuyin": "ㄙ ㄞˋ ㄆㄨˇ"}, {"surface": "Slack", "entity_id": "companies_intl:46", "start": 36, "end": 41, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "Slack", "en": "Slack", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "", "zhuyin": ""}]}
{"id": "ner-000437", "text": "上週末的家庭聚會聊得超開心。表哥剛從美式賣場掃了一堆東西回來，姑姑則說她在 SOGO 百貨買到妮維雅的特價組合超划算。我們還一起追了藍正龍的新戲，順便聽了張雨生的老歌，整個下午都很放鬆。", "register": "日常對話", "bucket": "M", "n_han": 81, "est_duration_s": 18.47, "has_english": true, "has_phonetic_entity": true, "n_substitutable": 4, "annotations": [{"surface": "美式賣場", "entity_id": "people_tw:432", "start": 18, "end": 22, "type": "PER", "region": "TW", "zh": "美式賣場", "en": "", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "měi shì mài chǎng", "zhuyin": "ㄇㄟˇ ㄕˋ ㄇㄞˋ ㄔㄤˇ"}, {"surface": "SOGO 百貨", "entity_id": "companies_tw:257", "start": 38, "end": 45, "type": "ORG", "region": "TW", "zh": "SOGO百貨", "en": "Pacific SOGO", "aliases": ["太平洋SOGO", "SOGO"], "pinyin": "bǎi huò", "zhuyin": "ㄅㄞˇ ㄏㄨㄛˋ"}, {"surface": "妮維雅", "entity_id": "companies_intl:583", "start": 47, "end": 50, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "妮維雅", "en": "Nivea", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "nī wéi yǎ", "zhuyin": "ㄋㄧ ㄨㄟˊ ㄧㄚˇ"}, {"surface": "藍正龍", "entity_id": "people_tw:365", "start": 66, "end": 69, "type": "PER", "region": "TW", "zh": "藍正龍", "en": "Blue Lan", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "lán zhèng lóng", "zhuyin": "ㄌㄢˊ ㄓㄥˋ ㄌㄨㄥˊ"}, {"surface": "張雨生", "entity_id": "people_tw:231", "start": 77, "end": 80, "type": "PER", "region": "TW", "zh": "張雨生", "en": "Tom Chang", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "zhāng yǔ shēng", "zhuyin": "ㄓㄤ ㄩˇ ㄕㄥ"}]}
{"id": "ner-001237", "text": "今天的產業焦點，我們把目光放在幾家具代表性的台灣企業。台塑集團的王文淵長期帶領石化版圖，是業界相當受矚目的人物。同一時間，正新與卜蜂分別在輪胎與食品領域穩紮穩打，撐起傳統產業的半邊天。值得一提的是，美國鋁業近期也釋出與亞洲供應鏈加強合作的訊號，顯示原物料市場的連動性正在升溫。", "register": "新聞報導", "bucket": "M", "n_han": 128, "est_duration_s": 28.72, "has_english": false, "has_phonetic_entity": true, "n_substitutable": 5, "annotations": [{"surface": "台塑集團", "entity_id": "companies_tw:129", "start": 27, "end": 31, "type": "ORG", "region": "TW", "zh": "台塑企業", "en": "Formosa Plastics Group", "aliases": ["台塑集團", "台塑四寶"], "pinyin": "tái sù qǐ yè", "zhuyin": "ㄊㄞˊ ㄙㄨˋ ㄑㄧˇ ㄧㄝˋ"}, {"surface": "王文淵", "entity_id": "people_tw:144", "start": 32, "end": 35, "type": "PER", "region": "TW", "zh": "王文淵", "en": "Wang Wen-yuan", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "wáng wén yuān", "zhuyin": "ㄨㄤˊ ㄨㄣˊ ㄩㄢ"}, {"surface": "正新", "entity_id": "companies_tw:236", "start": 61, "end": 63, "type": "ORG", "region": "TW", "zh": "正新", "en": "Cheng Shin Rubber", "aliases": ["正新橡膠", "瑪吉斯", "Maxxis"], "pinyin": "zhèng xīn", "zhuyin": "ㄓㄥˋ ㄒㄧㄣ"}, {"surface": "卜蜂", "entity_id": "companies_tw:303", "start": 64, "end": 66, "type": "ORG", "region": "TW", "zh": "卜蜂", "en": "Charoen Pokphand (Taiwan)", "aliases": ["卜蜂企業"], "pinyin": "bǔ fēng", "zhuyin": "ㄅㄨˇ ㄈㄥ"}, {"surface": "美國鋁業", "entity_id": "companies_intl:495", "start": 99, "end": 103, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "美國鋁業", "en": "Alcoa", "aliases": ["美鋁", "Alcoa"], "pinyin": "měi guó lǚ yè", "zhuyin": "ㄇㄟˇ ㄍㄨㄛˊ ㄌㄩˇ ㄧㄝˋ"}]}
{"id": "ner-001307", "text": "今天的財經連線，我們先看美股這邊。摩根大通的執行長勞埃德·布蘭克梵在受訪時表示，聯準會的政策路徑仍存在高度不確定性；與此同時，三星與超微也相繼釋出對下半年半導體景氣的看法，市場普遍解讀為謹慎中帶著一絲樂觀。", "register": "新聞報導", "bucket": "M", "n_han": 95, "est_duration_s": 21.27, "has_english": false, "has_phonetic_entity": true, "n_substitutable": 5, "annotations": [{"surface": "摩根大通", "entity_id": "companies_intl:145", "start": 17, "end": 21, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "摩根大通", "en": "JPMorgan Chase", "aliases": ["小摩", "摩根大通集團", "JPMorgan"], "pinyin": "mó gēn dà tōng", "zhuyin": "ㄇㄛˊ ㄍㄣ ㄉㄚˋ ㄊㄨㄥ"}, {"surface": "勞埃德·布蘭克梵", "entity_id": "people_intl:254", "start": 25, "end": 33, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "勞埃德·布蘭克梵", "en": "Lloyd Blankfein", "aliases": ["布蘭克梵"], "pinyin": "láo āi dé bù lán kè fàn", "zhuyin": "ㄌㄠˊ ㄞ ㄉㄜˊ ㄅㄨˋ ㄌㄢˊ ㄎㄜˋ ㄈㄢˋ"}, {"surface": "聯準會", "entity_id": "companies_intl:275", "start": 40, "end": 43, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "聯邦準備理事會", "en": "Federal Reserve", "aliases": ["聯準會", "美聯儲", "Fed", "聯邦準備"], "pinyin": "lián bāng zhǔn bèi lǐ shì huì", "zhuyin": "ㄌㄧㄢˊ ㄅㄤ ㄓㄨㄣˇ ㄅㄟˋ ㄌㄧˇ ㄕˋ ㄏㄨㄟˋ"}, {"surface": "三星", "entity_id": "companies_intl:78", "start": 63, "end": 65, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "三星", "en": "Samsung", "aliases": ["三星電子"], "pinyin": "sān xīng", "zhuyin": "ㄙㄢ ㄒㄧㄥ"}, {"surface": "超微", "entity_id": "companies_intl:11", "start": 66, "end": 68, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "超微", "en": "AMD", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "chāo wēi", "zhuyin": "ㄔㄠ ㄨㄟ"}]}
{"id": "ner-001767", "text": "歡迎回到節目，今天我們聊聊體育與娛樂的跨界。先說運動，菲爾普斯與內馬爾雖然來自完全不同的項目，卻都背負著國家的期待。再轉到音樂圈，巴德·邦尼用拉丁節奏席捲全球，而韓國的 Red Velvet 則靠著精緻的舞台，圈了一票死忠粉絲。這種跨界的能量，其實正在重新定義什麼叫做偶像。", "register": "訪談", "bucket": "M", "n_han": 113, "est_duration_s": 26.29, "has_english": true, "has_phonetic_entity": true, "n_substitutable": 4, "annotations": [{"surface": "菲爾普斯", "entity_id": "people_intl:497", "start": 27, "end": 31, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "菲爾普斯", "en": "Michael Phelps", "aliases": ["麥可·菲爾普斯", "費爾普斯", "飛魚"], "pinyin": "fēi ěr pǔ sī", "zhuyin": "ㄈㄟ ㄦˇ ㄆㄨˇ ㄙ"}, {"surface": "內馬爾", "entity_id": "people_intl:430", "start": 32, "end": 35, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "內馬爾", "en": "Neymar", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "nèi mǎ ěr", "zhuyin": "ㄋㄟˋ ㄇㄚˇ ㄦˇ"}, {"surface": "巴德·邦尼", "entity_id": "people_intl:897", "start": 65, "end": 70, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "巴德·邦尼", "en": "Bad Bunny", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "bā dé bāng ní", "zhuyin": "ㄅㄚ ㄉㄜˊ ㄅㄤ ㄋㄧˊ"}, {"surface": "Red Velvet", "entity_id": "people_intl:764", "start": 85, "end": 95, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "Red Velvet", "en": "Red Velvet", "aliases": ["Red Velvet"], "pinyin": "", "zhuyin": ""}]}
{"id": "ner-003602", "text": "今天的國際要聞一次看。據路透報導，拉夫羅夫在最新一輪會談中表態審慎；能源方面，盧克石油與法國燃氣蘇伊士的合作案傳出新進展；娛樂版則有蕾哈娜與少女時代同台的消息，引爆社群討論熱潮。", "register": "新聞報導", "bucket": "M", "n_han": 82, "est_duration_s": 18.47, "has_english": false, "has_phonetic_entity": true, "n_substitutable": 6, "annotations": [{"surface": "路透", "entity_id": "companies_intl:182", "start": 12, "end": 14, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "路透", "en": "Reuters", "aliases": ["湯森路透"], "pinyin": "lù tòu", "zhuyin": "ㄌㄨˋ ㄊㄡˋ"}, {"surface": "拉夫羅夫", "entity_id": "people_intl:24", "start": 17, "end": 21, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "拉夫羅夫", "en": "Sergey Lavrov", "aliases": ["拉夫羅夫外長"], "pinyin": "lā fū luó fū", "zhuyin": "ㄌㄚ ㄈㄨ ㄌㄨㄛˊ ㄈㄨ"}, {"surface": "盧克石油", "entity_id": "companies_intl:449", "start": 39, "end": 43, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "盧克石油", "en": "Lukoil", "aliases": ["盧克歐爾"], "pinyin": "lú kè shí yóu", "zhuyin": "ㄌㄨˊ ㄎㄜˋ ㄕˊ ㄧㄡˊ"}, {"surface": "法國燃氣蘇伊士", "entity_id": "companies_intl:516", "start": 44, "end": 51, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "法國燃氣蘇伊士", "en": "Engie", "aliases": ["Engie", "蘇伊士集團"], "pinyin": "fǎ guó rán qì sū yī shì", "zhuyin": "ㄈㄚˇ ㄍㄨㄛˊ ㄖㄢˊ ㄑㄧˋ ㄙㄨ ㄧ ㄕˋ"}, {"surface": "蕾哈娜", "entity_id": "people_intl:692", "start": 66, "end": 69, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "蕾哈娜", "en": "Rihanna", "aliases": ["Rihanna"], "pinyin": "lěi hā nà", "zhuyin": "ㄌㄟˇ ㄏㄚ ㄋㄚˋ"}, {"surface": "少女時代", "entity_id": "people_intl:759", "start": 70, "end": 74, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "少女時代", "en": "Girls' Generation", "aliases": ["SNSD", "Girls' Generation"], "pinyin": "shào nǚ shí dài", "zhuyin": "ㄕㄠˋ ㄋㄩˇ ㄕˊ ㄉㄞˋ"}]}
{"id": "ner-005385", "text": "下午的科技訪談非常精彩。主持人先請黃仁勳談談 AI 算力的瓶頸，他講得深入淺出。接著話題轉到供應鏈，奇力新與台塑化的代表分別從被動元件和石化原料的角度補充，讓大家看到一台裝置背後牽動的產業有多廣。最後是國際視野，永明金融的分析師說明資金如何流向這些題材。", "register": "訪談", "bucket": "M", "n_han": 115, "est_duration_s": 26.02, "has_english": true, "has_phonetic_entity": true, "n_substitutable": 4, "annotations": [{"surface": "黃仁勳", "entity_id": "people_intl:230", "start": 17, "end": 20, "type": "PER", "region": "INTL", "zh": "黃仁勳", "en": "Jensen Huang", "aliases": ["Jensen Huang"], "pinyin": "huáng rén xūn", "zhuyin": "ㄏㄨㄤˊ ㄖㄣˊ ㄒㄩㄣ"}, {"surface": "奇力新", "entity_id": "companies_tw:62", "start": 50, "end": 53, "type": "ORG", "region": "TW", "zh": "奇力新", "en": "Chilisin", "aliases": ["奇力新電子"], "pinyin": "qí lì xīn", "zhuyin": "ㄑㄧˊ ㄌㄧˋ ㄒㄧㄣ"}, {"surface": "台塑化", "entity_id": "companies_tw:128", "start": 54, "end": 57, "type": "ORG", "region": "TW", "zh": "台塑化", "en": "Formosa Petrochemical", "aliases": ["台塑石化"], "pinyin": "tái sù huà", "zhuyin": "ㄊㄞˊ ㄙㄨˋ ㄏㄨㄚˋ"}, {"surface": "永明金融", "entity_id": "companies_intl:254", "start": 106, "end": 110, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "永明金融", "en": "Sun Life", "aliases": ["永明", "加拿大永明", "Sun Life"], "pinyin": "yǒng míng jīn róng", "zhuyin": "ㄩㄥˇ ㄇㄧㄥˊ ㄐㄧㄣ ㄖㄨㄥˊ"}]}
{"id": "ner-006937", "text": "說到運動品牌，愛迪達跟迪卡儂走的路線真的差很多。愛迪達主打的是潮流跟聯名，迪卡儂則是 CP 值取向，東西便宜又實用。我自己跑步的裝備幾乎都在迪卡儂買，但球鞋還是會挑愛迪達，畢竟穿起來比較有面子。", "register": "產品評論", "bucket": "M", "n_han": 85, "est_duration_s": 19.57, "has_english": true, "has_phonetic_entity": true, "n_substitutable": 6, "annotations": [{"surface": "愛迪達", "entity_id": "companies_intl:638", "start": 7, "end": 10, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "愛迪達", "en": "Adidas", "aliases": ["Adidas", "愛迪達斯"], "pinyin": "ài dí dá", "zhuyin": "ㄞˋ ㄉㄧˊ ㄉㄚˊ"}, {"surface": "迪卡儂", "entity_id": "companies_intl:572", "start": 11, "end": 14, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "迪卡儂", "en": "Decathlon", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "dí kǎ nóng", "zhuyin": "ㄉㄧˊ ㄎㄚˇ ㄋㄨㄥˊ"}, {"surface": "愛迪達", "entity_id": "companies_intl:638", "start": 24, "end": 27, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "愛迪達", "en": "Adidas", "aliases": ["Adidas", "愛迪達斯"], "pinyin": "ài dí dá", "zhuyin": "ㄞˋ ㄉㄧˊ ㄉㄚˊ"}, {"surface": "迪卡儂", "entity_id": "companies_intl:572", "start": 37, "end": 40, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "迪卡儂", "en": "Decathlon", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "dí kǎ nóng", "zhuyin": "ㄉㄧˊ ㄎㄚˇ ㄋㄨㄥˊ"}, {"surface": "迪卡儂", "entity_id": "companies_intl:572", "start": 70, "end": 73, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "迪卡儂", "en": "Decathlon", "aliases": [], "pinyin": "dí kǎ nóng", "zhuyin": "ㄉㄧˊ ㄎㄚˇ ㄋㄨㄥˊ"}, {"surface": "愛迪達", "entity_id": "companies_intl:638", "start": 82, "end": 85, "type": "ORG", "region": "INTL", "zh": "愛迪達", "en": "Adidas", "aliases": ["Adidas", "愛迪達斯"], "pinyin": "ài dí dá", "zhuyin": "ㄞˋ ㄉㄧˊ ㄉㄚˊ"}]}
